<h2><a class="mozTocH2" name="mozTocId982301"></a>Only a <strong>SINGLE</strong> scientific mistake is enough to prove that whole Islam is fake</h2>
<p>In conclusion, even a single scientific mistake in the Quran is significant, as it challenges the notion of 100%  Allah's perfection and cast doubt on the authenticity of the entire Islamic belief system.</p>
